== Overview ==
A powerful Federate shield that, unlike most Federate equipment, is compact enough to be equipped to some Cybot chassis.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Photonic Array can be found in the storage bunker of [[Firebase (Talsia)|Firebases]] in the [[Alpha Sector]] of the [[Talsia|Talsian Warfront]].
